every step you take is filled with dread. While the gameplay is rooted in fear, it maintains a sense of fun and excitement, making it as exhilarating as it is terrifying.", "short_description": "Extinction Facility is a VR horror fan game inspired by the eerie and intense vibes of \"Big Scary\" and \"Scary Baboon.\" While it draws from these chilling influences, it offers a unique, heart-racing experience as players navigate through a dark, terrifying facility. The game balances fear and fun, backed by an amazing community that makes the suspenseful adventure worth diving into."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://ezra-1-shop.fourthwall.com/pages/privacy-policy-19372f45-86af-40b1-ae25-e3deababc97a", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "PanzeeStudios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://ezra-1-shop.fourthwall.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "27129942736652609"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1037680018094200"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1037680018094200"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1729712220, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1037680018094200"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "27113413788305504", "version": "0.